<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Forum | Topics</title>
	<link rel = "stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.4.0/css/font-awesome.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/pure/0.6.0/pure-min.css">
	 <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/pure/0.6.0/grids-responsive-min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
	<div id="wrapper">
		<header>
			<div class="custom-wrapper pure-g" id="menu">
	    	<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-3">
	        <div class="pure-menu">
	            <a href="/" class="pure-menu-heading custom-brand">thoughtBrew</a>
	            <a href="#" class="custom-toggle" id="toggle"><s class="bar"></s><s class="bar"></s></a>
	        </div>
	    	</div>
    		<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-3">
    	  	<div class="pure-menu pure-menu-horizontal custom-can-transform">
    	 		</div>
    		</div>
   			 <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-3">
        		<div class="pure-menu pure-menu-horizontal custom-menu-3 custom-can-transform">
            	<ul class="pure-menu-list">
                <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="/forum/topics" class="pure-menu-link">New Topic</a></li>
                <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="/forum/topics/popular" class="pure-menu-link">Popular</a></li>
                <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="/forum/comments/recent" class="pure-menu-link">Recent</a></li>
                <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="/" class="pure-menu-link">Logout</a></li>
           		 </ul>
       			 </div>
    		</div>
			</div>
	</header>
	<div id="main">
		<div class="pure-g">
			<div class="pure-u-sm-hidden pure-u-md-1-4 pure-u-lg-1-4" id="align-right">
				<div id="text">
				<p><em>Purge, percolate, or hoard. Create new ideas, collaborate with your team, and move forward with your favorites. Distill what you like and dump the rest. THOUGHTbrew eliminates stagnant ideas before you have time to reconsider them. Less decision-making means better results. Get to great faster with THOUGHTbrew.</em></p>
			</div>
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1-12 pure-u-md-1-12 pure-u-lg-1-12">
			</div>
		<div id="content" class="pure-u-11-12 pure-u-md-2-3 pure-u-lg-2-3">
			<h1><%=type%> Topics</h1>
				<%Object.keys(topics).forEach(function(key){ %>
					<a name="<%=topics[key].id%>"></a>
							<ul id="topics">						
							<li><a href='/forum/topics/<%=topics[key].title%>'>
								<h3> <%=topics[key].title%></h3> </a>
							</li>
							<li>	
								<form action='/forum/topics/<%=topics[key].id%>?_method=PUT' method="POST">
									<input class="hidden" name="user_id" value="<%=topics[key].user_id%>">
									<input class="hidden" name="id" value="<%=topics[key].id%>">
									<button id = "vote">likes <%=topics[key].votes%></button>
								</form>
							</li>
						<br><img id="user-image" src="<%=topics[key].image%>"><em> created by <%=topics[key].user_name%></em>
				</ul>
			<%})%>		
			</div>
<footer id="comment">
	<div class="pure-g">
			<div class="pure-u-sm-hidden pure-u-md-1-3 pure-u-lg-1-3">
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-2-3 pure-u-lg-2-3">
	<form action='/forum/topics' method='POST'>
			<input type = "text" name="title" placeholder="add new title topic" required>
			<input  type = "text" name="name" placeholder="username" required>
			<button>Add</button>
		</form>
	</div>
</div>
</footer>
</div>
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.1.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>